OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry today with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunshine across the region. Feeling
OL,7,Fvery warm with light winds at first,
OL,8,Fbut the breeze will pick up through
OL,9,Fthe afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FTurning cloudy across
OL,12,Fnorthern parts of the region with a
OL,13,Ffew spots of light rain over the Peak
OL,14,FDistrict. However, dry elsewhere with
OL,15,Fclear skies and a mild night.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FStaying cloudy across the far
OL,18,Fnorth, but strong sunshine elsewhere
OL,19,Fwhich could turn hazy at times. Winds
OL,20,Feasing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
