OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith plenty of sunshine next week,
OL,7,Fturning hazy at times. Becoming
OL,8,Fincreasingly hot with light winds and
OL,9,Fwarm nights.
